          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The new TIARA array is designed to exploit",
                "such transfer reactions with radioactive beams, using",
                "inverse kinematics with hydrogen polymer targets.",
                "The TIARA array is a highly efficient particle detector",
                "for almost all angles."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The TIARA barrel consists of eight silicon",
                "strip detectors, each with four resistive strips",
                "mounted along the beam direction. Each detector has a",
                "wafer size of 96.8*24.6 mm**2 and an active area of",
                "94.8*22.6 mm**2, with strips 5.65 mm wide. All",
                "detectors in the annular arrays are 500 mum in",
                "thickness."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The VAMOS magnetic spectrometer operated in",
                "dispersive mode."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".For gamma-ray detection, four of the segmented-",
                "clover Ge detectors from EXOGAM, were mounted with",
                "their front faces forming a cube around the target,",
                " 50 mm from the beam spot.",
                "The data acquisition systems for TIARA, VAMOS AND",
                "EXOGAM operated separately, each with access to a",
                "common event counter and the data streams were merged",
                "in real time."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Inverse kinematics"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Correction for Doppler and add-back effects was",
                "has been developed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
